cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

This paper presents a novel solution for object recognition and pose estimation in robotic manipulation scenarios. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also heavily relies on deep learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves semantic segmentation, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper's focus on improving the speed and robustness of perception systems could also suggest cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
